In re D.P. et al.; D.O., Appellant; Franklin County Children Services, Appellee.

[Cite as In re D.P., 109 Ohio St.3d 207, 2006-Ohio-2185.]

(No. 2005-2142 Submitted April 11, 2006 Decided May 17, 2006.) John T. Ryerson, for appellant. Robert J. McClaren, for appellee.

{¶ 1} The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed on the authority of In re C.R., 108 Ohio St.3d 369, 2006-Ohio-1191, 843 N.E.2d 1188.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell and Lanzinger, JJ., concur.
